      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "TRACEY TARO (1) has been in the placings at her last two runs, most recently when third (30.05) in a Grade 5 over 520m at this track. Has good speed and is aided by the cherry draw. Better than latest and can atone here. ZIPPING EVANIA (2) produced a moderate effort last time when sixth at Richmond over 622m behind West Rock Casey (35.97) in a NG. Form from her last run is proving strong. Has ability and is one of the better chances. RITZA KRIS (6) finished sixth last time at this track but could not have been more impressive before that in her excellent 22.20 win at Bulli over 400m. Must include on winning run two back. RAYMAR SHAME (8) has claims again if she runs up to the latest effort.",
